text: Archer Rock is a barren rock within Marblehead Channel in Marblehead, Massachusetts. It is west of Cat Island (Salem City) and far northeast of Marblehead Neck. (Coordinates: Lat. = 42.513'N, Lon. = 70.824'W) Category:Marblehead, Massachusetts Category:Islands of Essex County, Massachusetts Category:Islands of Massachusetts
title: Archer Rock
